{"tid":2439412,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個鬼佬廢老一隻股票賺咗93.6 億... 求起底","createTime":"2021-03-09T08:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T23:18:36.000Z","uid":275872,"like":139,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"fbbd8444f087a03df4041a9ba13d82878437c072","tid":2439412,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>股神巴菲特重倉雪佛龍 不足10周賺近百億</strong><br />\n<br />\n股神巴菲特投資旗艦巴郡2020年表現相對失色，但去年底公布，重倉跨國能源巨企雪佛龍(Chevron)，這筆投資在不足10周，回報達12億美元(約93.6億港元)。<br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，巴郡在2020年第4季的報告透露，公司從2020年第3季開始建倉雪佛龍，截至2020年12月底，共持有雪佛龍2.5%股份，市值41億美元。由於油價在今年初持續上漲，帶動雪佛龍股價攀升，今年以來大漲29%，讓巴郡持有的雪佛龍市值達到53億美元。換句話說，股神這筆投資在不足10周，就獲得12億美元的帳面收益。"},{"pid":"4efc875b792a75912c1775f5b9300bdee2b80659","tid":2439412,"uid":275872,"like":31,"dislike":6,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210309/photo/bkn-20210309124748824-0309_00842_001_01p.jpg?20210309144856\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210309%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210309124748824-0309_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20210309144856&h=ff769936&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"068ab7adac359f64e0cd2f42860b880fc53c25c4","tid":2439412,"uid":275872,"like":71,"dislike":4,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:50:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://money18.on.cc/finnews/content/exp/bkn-20210309124748824-0309_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Ffinnews%2Fcontent%2Fexp%2Fbkn-20210309124748824-0309_00842_001.html&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhywpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=bd4e9d44\" target=\"_blank\">https://money18.on.cc/finnews/content/exp/bkn-20210309124748824-0309_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我